function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

-- Wounded sailor dialogue
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CON_SAILOR, idActor)

end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

-- Sailor corpse comment
local nSailor = Hydra.GetRandomInt(1, 2);
	
	if nSailor == 1 then
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CON_CORPSE_01, idActorPlayer)
		else
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CON_CORPSE_02, idActorPlayer)
	end
		
end
